title: Mystery Train
description: Finn and Jake get wrapped up in a high speed whodunit!

title: People Pleaser
description: Blossom neglects her promise to Bubbles when she takes on too many things leaving Buttercup and Bubbles to fend for themselves.

title: Rock On
description: The Looney Builders are hired by Mac and Tosh Gopher to build them a home underground. Daffy can't remove rocks from the area fast enough and fails to ask for help.

title: Knock It Off
description: When the Professor's college roommate sees his old pal's brilliant creations, he decides to cash in on the popularity of the Powerpuffs.

title: Thomas' Promise
description: When Thomas and Diesel both want to deliver the same load to Whiff's Recycling Plant, Thomas suggests they each take half of the load, but Diesel turns it into a race.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Perder la cabeza
description: El equipo Tennyson se da una vuelta por una reunión familiar alternativa, y Ben se encuentra con mucho más que primos excéntricos, concretamente con Kevin 11 y los Hermanos Bicho, cuyo último invento alocado desata una serie de intercambios de cabeza divertidísimos entre todos los grupos.

title: Historias de miedo
description: Durante la fiesta de Halloween de la banda, iUnikitty descubre que Rick no le teme a nada! Para contagiarle el espíritu festivo, Unikitty cuenta sus propias ideas de lo que es una historia espeluznante, con la esperanza de asustar al inconmovible de Rick por una vez. iPero cada cuento es aún más espeluznante (y más tonto) que el anterior!

title: The Curse of Elmore
description: When Gumball's schoolfriend Leslie finds an old video tape, the creepy mystery of Elmore's ghostly past unfolds. Featuring spooky and hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Green Wing
description: When volunteering at a retirement home, Buttercup meets an old woman who claims she used to be a superhero.

title: Sneakerheads
description: Apple & Onion need a Last Will and Testament if they are to protect their belongings from the state.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Capullos de Rosa
description: Steven recibe una visita sorpresa de algunos viejos amigos y una introducción aún más sorprendente a algunos nuevos.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Ghost Princess
description: Finn and Jake try to solve Ghost Princess' unsolved murder.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Elmore's Most Wanted
description: Gumball's dad has been revealed as "Elmore's Most Wanted" - but when the Chief of Police tries to investigate, things do not go according to plan. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Patients
description: Clarence must somehow navigate the mind-numbing boredom of a doctor's office waiting room to earn the ultimate prize - candy from the reception desk candy jar.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Into the Overpast
description: Craig and The Green Poncho travel to the Other Side of the Creek where Craig learns Green Poncho's shocking origin story.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Eater
description: It's Halloween and Apple's not feeling quite right. He takes Onion into the dark depths to find out why.

title: El Corazon
description: El señor Robinson intenta recuperar la amistad de Gumball y Darwin y falla una y otra vez.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Neighborhood Grill
description: Clarence is so troubled by the sight of his teacher in a social setting outside of school, he can't stop himself from intruding on her doomed blind date.

title: Forced Kin
description: A terrible, evil menace from outer space descends upon Townville. The girls must fight evil with evil so they seek the advice of Mojo Jojo.

title: Rose Buds
description: Steven gets a surprise visit from some old friends, and an even more surprising introduction to some new ones.

title: Dia de Elecciones
description: Manzana se presenta como candidato a alcalde.

title: Una sola rosa palida
description: Steven ayuda a Perla a encontrar su teléfono.

title: El Desastre
description: Gumball y Darwin cuidan y luego pierden a la hermanita de Penny.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Voleibol
description: Steven está decidido a ayudar a la Perla original de Diamante Rosa para sanar la cicatriz en su rostro.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Pequena Escuela Madre
description: Bienvenidos a la Pequeña Escuela Madre, un lugar en la Tierra donde Gemas de todo el universo pueden aprender a vivir juntas pacíficamente. Pero hay una Gema que se rehúsa a asistir.

title: Buzz In
description: Bizzy Buzzard's mom hires The Looney Builders to build her family a new nest. Bizzy wants to help but keeps getting in the way creating all sorts of problems for the crew.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: All Chalked Up
description: Him tricks Bubbles into bringing her chalk drawings to life, who then proceed to wreak havoc in Townsville.

title: Onion Trade
description: A boy trade between Steven and Onion escalates to epic proportions.

title: Cual es tu problema
description: Amatista convence a Steven de que se tome un día libre.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: La noche que Ben Tennyson vino al pueblo
description: El equipo Tennyson viaja a Wheeler, "la ciudad minera más animada de la Ruta 66". Pero cuando Ben se pone paranoico con la idea de que el Caballero por Siempre lo esté persiguiendo, debe tratar de convencer a su familia al mismo tiempo que evita que su nuevo enemigo destruya la ciudad.

title: Dama de honor
description: Steven tiene una gran sorpresa para las Gemas de Cristal.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Song of Sodor
description: When Nia suggests adding a song to spice up Sir Topham Hatt's new bench unveiling, he calls upon her to write a song for the ceremony, but Nia soon finds she may have bitten off more than she can sing.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Manzana, Concentrate
description: Manzana ayuda a Cebollín a cumplir su sueño de competir en un programa de pastelería.

title: Caballero TV 2
description: Batman y el Comisionado Gordon hacen una pijamada para mirar sus programas de televisión favoritos.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: El Agente
description: En una misión escolar super secreta, Gumball se comporta como cierto sofisticado agente secreto británico.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Lista de Traviesos
description: Es Nochebuena y Brock está emocionado por la visita de Santa Claus. Mientras se prepara para que Master Frown le lea un cuento para dormir, Unikitty y la banda irrumpen en su casa. Están ahí para evitar que Master Frown arruine más Navidades. Frown se declara inocente, pero Unikitty y la banda cuentan las historias de las Navidades pasadas que ya arruinó. ¿Frown probará su inocencia o se pondrá a la cabeza de la lista de los traviesos?

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Slumber Party Panic
description: Finn must keep his promise to Princess Bubblegum and cover up the zombie problem they've created.

title: Baby Bears on a Plane
description: The Baby Bears have an adventure in the sky while aboard a plane to Sweden. But when the baby Bears are forced to sit in different sections of the plan, things get a bit haywire for everyone on board.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Steven the Sword Fighter
description: Pearl tries to teach Steven the art of sword-fighting using a holographic version of himself.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: So Many Birthdays
description: So Many Birthdays: Steven learns that the Crystal Gems are thousands of years old and decides to make up for all the thousands of birthdays they've missed.

title: Azulejo
description: Steven cuestiona los motivos de una misteriosa fusión que de repente se presenta en su casa.

title: Mision Espacial Peligrosa
description: Después de la explosión de su nave espacial, Unikitty y la banda flotan indefensos por el espacio. Mientras tratan de formular un plan que los lleve a casa a salvo, vuelven a ver qué parte de la responsabilidad por la destrucción de su nave tiene cada uno. ¿Lograrán volver a casa? Y lo que es más importante, ¿quién tendrá la culpa si no lo hacen?

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ducks
description: Blippi gets up close and personal with Declan the Duck in his quest to find how ducks float! Under the water, above the water, through feather tunnels and tooting air bubbles, Blippi and Declan work together to discover the answer.

title: Truffle Season
description: It's Truffle Season, Apple and Onion are Truffle Hunters and they will stop at nothing to taste a truffle.

title: La pregunta
description: Steven les muestra a unas gemas citadinas cómo vivían los vaqueros.

title: Jewel of the Aisle/Super Zeroes
description: Jewel of the Isle: A crook hides a huge diamond in a box of the girls' favorite cereal. But how can he trick the girls into giving him some cereal in order to get the jewel back?/Super Zeroes: The girls don't think they have enough superhero accessories like those found in the comic books. They begin to emulate their favorite characters, complete with gadgets and gizmos.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: The Last Donnycorn
description: When Donny the Unicorn is hunted by a seemingly unstoppable foe, the Powerpuff Girls have to find a way to save him before it's too late!

title: Dia de los Trabajos
description: Robin obliga a los demás Titanes a olvidar sus sueños y a conseguir trabajos normales y aburridos.

title: The Time Capsule
description: Worried he'll one day forget all his favorite memories, Craig creates a time capsule to remember them all.

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Bati-Kitty
description: La banda está lavando ropa en la lavandería local, cuando Unikitty encuentra el uniforme de Batman mezclado con su ropa. Embriagada al ver lo genial que es el disfraz, Unikitty adopta la personalidad de Batman y comienza a luchar contra el crimen. Cuando accidentalmente hace que Master Frown intensifique su actividad delictiva, Unikitty necesitará la ayuda de sus amigos, vestidos todos como Robin, para detenerlo.

title: Birds Nest
description: A storm has destroyed Jodie the Blue Jays bird nest! Good thing Blippi and FETCH are there to help. While FETCH is on egg-sitting duty, Jodie and Blippi go on a heist mission to acquire the materials needed to rebuild. It's never an impossible mission when friends work together!

title: Splitsville
description: The girls learn to appreciate each others's style after having to each fight solo.

title: Titanes Clasicos
description: Para demostrar su punto de vista sobre los dibujos animados clásicos de superhéroes, iControl Freak envía a los Titanes a una versión antigua de Jóvenes Titanes en Acción!

title: Falafel's Car Keys
description: Apple & Onion are deemed responsible enough to borrow Falafel's car for their first road trip together. Nothing will go wrong, and they're going to make sure of that… by getting some practice in.

title: Guidance
description: Amethyst has been helping Little Homeschool Gems find jobs on the boardwalk, but Steven isn't sure about her approach.

title: La Red
description: Gumball y Darwin le dan a Nicole un curso intensivo de computación.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Fortachones
description: Manzana y Cebollín se inscriben en un gimnasio para adquirir la fuerza de siete personas juntas.

title: El Desfile
description: Unikitty planea un desfile para celebrar lo que cada uno tiene de único, idonde cada uno diseñará sus propias carrozas personalizadas! Pero Master Frown planea arruinar el desfile con una carroza súper deprimente. El desfile se convierte en un duelo intenso (y de una lentitud divertidísima) de coche contra carroza mientras Unikitty y los demás intentan derribar a Master Frown! ¿Le pondrá un freno Unikitty al complot a baja velocidad de Frown?

title: Splash Song
description: Ella is drawing a bus when she lets her imagination runs wild!

title: Ahora nos estamos separando
description: Perla cuenta una historia.

title: Lion 2: The Movie
description: Steven and Connie try to ride the Lion to the movie theater but Lion has other ideas.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Little Homeschool
description: Welcome to Little Homeschool, a place on earth where Gems from all over the universe can come learn how to live together peacefully! But there's one Gem who refuses to attend.

title: Nacion Xingo
description: Kevin 11 aumenta la potencia de Xingo -que queda libre y causa estragos en otros programas de televisión-, y Ben es el responsable de detener a los dos.

title: Princess Monster Wife
description: When Ooo's princesses start losing body parts left and right, Finn and Jake investigate.

title: Recycle Stomp
description: Mei, the children and some animals are in the park collecting trash to recycle!

title: The Need for Feed/The Zipline Sisters of Treetop Woods
description: MacBarm is bringing food to his hungry chickens, that is, until all of the food falls out of his truck./Grandma and her twin sister want to recreate their old zipline act, but quickly discover that the zipline no longer exists!

title: Bluebird
description: Steven questions the motives of a mysterious fusion that suddenly shows up at his house.

title: Volleyball
description: Steven is determined to help Pink Diamond's original Pearl heal the scar on her face.

title: Him Diddle Riddle
description: The Powerpuff Girls must solve a series of Him's riddles to keep the Professor from having to pay.

title: Lars and the Cool Kids
description: Steven and Lars get to hang out with the cool kids in town, but their teenage shenanigans get them into magical trouble.

title: Secret Origin of the Batwheels
description: When Batman, Robin, and Batgirl are all captured, the Batcomputer brings the Bat-Vehicles to life. Now the newly-minted Batwheels must defend the Batcave and face off with the Legion of Zoom… all without Batman's help!

title: Stray Bullet
description: In order to save an innocent squirrel, Bubbles gives him a dash of Chemical X, giving him some super squirrel powers.

title: 15 Minutes of Fame
description: When Bubbles' video goes viral, she goes to great lengths to maintain her status as a big-time director.

title: Entremedias
description: Manzana y Cebollín se pierden debajo de las tablas de madera del suelo y deben encontrar la salida.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: La Academia
description: Robin inventa el Premio Joven Titán en un esfuerzo por lograr que sus compañeros de equipo limpien la Torre.

title: La Fabrica
description: Gumball y Darwin salvan la Fábrica de Arcoíris.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Y Xingo era su Nombre
description: Cuando la nueva aplicación Xingo aparece misteriosamente en la tableta de Gwen, Ben no puede evitarlo y la activa a pesar de la desaprobación de su prima. Así, lanza una trampa que transporta a Ben al mundo animado y a Xingo de vuelta al mundo real.

title: The Audition
description: The Bears audition to be the next mascot for their favorite cereal. They get so caught up in the process that their competitiveness gets the best of them.

title: Captain Craboo
description: The Bears are reunited with their pet crab, Captain Craboo. But after an unfortunate run-in with Nom Nom, the Bears may lose their pet forever.

title: Castles and Kitties
description: Score Creeper traps the gang in a fantasy role playing game where they must follow a complex set of rules to win their freedom.

title: Filthy Rich
description: What does it take to be truly content? Whatever it takes, Apple and Onion are going to achieve it.

title: Unos y Ceros
description: Los Titanes construyen un robot con inteligencia artificial para que elabore una pizza que nunca antes fue hecha.

title: Henchman
description: While trying to rescue a helpless stranger, Finn becomes Marceline's slave.

title: Tongue Tied
description: Uncle Grandpa helps a shy kid gain confidence.

title: Miedo en la Familia
description: Ben y Gwen están ansiosos por que el Omni-Copter llegue a las Grandes Pirámides. Pero cuando el mal tiempo interrumpe su vuelo, pronto se enfrentan cara a cara con Neblina y sus engendros: iLa familia Niebla!

title: Manzana Podrida
description: Manzana y Cebollín tratan de convencer al papá de Cebollín de que Manzana no es una mala influencia.

title: Consejos
description: Amatista ha estado ayudando a las Gemas de Pequeña Escuela Madre a encontrar trabajo, pero Steven no está seguro de su enfoque.

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: That's the Way the Windmill Blows!/Mecha Machine Makers!
description: The windmill isn't turning, which means Sunny Field Farm has no power. The windmill needs to turn again so Zee can launch his rocket!/Izzy and Timmy are making a bird caller for Grandma, but have trouble connecting pieces of their machine.

title: Boogie Frights/Abracadaver
description: Boogie Frights: The Boogie Man creates perpetual night by launching a huge disco ball to block out the sun. While evil creatures are dancing and destroying in the dark, the Powerpuff Girls plot to crash the ball./Abracadaver: Al Lusion, the old-time Townsville magician, pulls off his greatest stunt yet when he comes back from the dead as the zombie Abracadaver to haunt Townsville.
